Hey there, Would you like to see what's in these files?

Whew. so glad to see these! You’ve heard about Leviathan, right? We’re all Leviathan fans around here.  

These files hold some of my research on Leviathan. So let’s see what we have here.
Wait, what’s going on? This is illegible. Everything’s scrambled, Finally got these back and now they’re not legible.

That looks challenging, but it’s something I can definitely help you with. Solving cryptology puzzles is one of my hobbies. First thing we’ll need is this. 
hmmm, there’s so much interesting material here! I see you’ve been keeping a dossier about leviathan!  I know  a bit about this illustrious figure myself.
Yes. Leviathan is one of our ancestors. He’s a hero of mine.
Well this might be handy. It turns out that what we’re looking at is an instruction for the Riley Maze app. It’s called Push.
So cool.   I remember finding that in an old folder that belonged to Leviathan. What does it do?
Riley can use it in the maze to push walls out of her way. It’s going to be essential in getting her past this obstacle.
Well this is a good development! Let’s go back to RileyMaze and see if Riley needs more help.
